==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{philosophy}} The state of existing together concurrently.
#: Example: ''The properties of redness and juiciness have '''compresence''' in apples.''

====Synonyms====
* [[coexistence]]
* [[concurrency]]
* [[copresence]]
* [[togetherness]]

